irami || || G. N. Velumani || [[K. R. Vijaya]], [[Jaya Guhanathan|Jaya]] ||25th Film\n|-\n| [[Dheivam]] || Subramaniyam ||[[M. A. Thirumugam]] || [[Gemini Ganesan]], [[K. R. Vijaya]], [[A. V. M. Rajan]], [[Sowcar Janaki]], [[R. Muthuraman]], [[Jaya Guhanathan|Jaya]] ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"12\" | 1973\n| [[Ganga Gowri (1973 film)|Ganga Gowri]] || Mahadevan ||[[B. R. Panthulu]] || [[Gemini Ganesan]], [[Jayalalithaa]], [[Jayanthi (actress)|Jayanthi]], [[Kumari Padmini]] ||\n|-\n| [[Arangetram (film)|Arangetram]] || Thangavelu ||[[K. Balachander]] || [[Prameela]], [[S. V. Subbaiah]], [[Kamal Haasan]], [[Jayachitra]], [[M. N. Rajam]], [[Jayasudha]] ||\n|-\n| [[Bharatha Vilas]] || Shankar ||[[A. C. Tirulokchandar]] || [[Sivaji Ganesan]], [[K. R. Vijaya]], [[Devika]], [[Major Sundarrajan]], [[Jayachitra]], [[Jayasudha]] ||\n|-\n| [[Rajaraja Cholan]] || Prince [[Rajendra Chola I]] ||[[A. P. Nagarajan]] || [[Sivaji Ganesan]], [[R. Muthuraman]], [[Lakshmi (actress)|Lakshmi]], [[C. R. Vijayakumari]] ||\n|-\n| Shanmugapriya ||  || K. Krishnamurthy || [[R. Muthuraman]], [[Jaya Guhanathan|Jaya]] || Guest Appearance\n|-\n| [[Ponnukku Thanga Manasu]] || Ramu ||[[Devaraj\u2013Mohan]] || [[Jayachitra]], [[Vijayakumar (actor)|Vijayakumar]], [[Vidhubala]] ||\n|-\n| Sondham || ||[[A. C. Tirulokchandar]] || [[R. Muthuraman]], [[K. R. Vijaya]], [[Prameela]] ||\n|-\n| [[Thirumalai Deivam]] || Lord Vishnu/Srinivasan ||[[A. P. Nagarajan]] || [[Gemini Ganesan]], [[R. Muthuraman]], [[A. V. M. Rajan]], [[K. B. Sundarambal]], [[Lakshmi (actress)|Lakshmi]], [[Srividya]], [[C. R. Vijayakumari]] ||\n|-\n| [[Kattila Thottila]] || Sambhasivam || Malliyam Rajagopal || [[Gemini Ganesan]], [[Bhanumathi Ramakrishna|P. Bhanumathi]], [[Kalpana (Kannada actress)|Kalpana]], [[Master Sekhar]] ||\n|-\n| [[Karaikkal Ammaiyar (film)|Karaikkal Ammaiyar]] || Lord Shiva ||[[A. P. Nagarajan]] || [[K. B. Sundarambal]], [[Lakshmi (actress)|Lakshmi]], [[R. Muthuraman]], [[Srividya]] ||\n|-\n| Pennai Nambungal || || B. V. 