a]] ||\n|-\n| Pennai Solli Kutramillai || ||[[S. P. Muthuraman]] || [[Fatafat Jayalaxmi]], [[Y. Vijaya]] ||\n|-\n| Perumaikkuriyaval || ||[[Ra. Sankaran]] || Padmapriya, [[Fatafat Jayalaxmi]] ||\n|-\n| [[Kavikkuyil]] || ||[[Devaraj\u2013Mohan]] || [[Rajinikanth]], [[Sridevi]] ||\n|-\n| Sorgam Naragam || || R. Thyagarajan || [[Fatafat Jayalaxmi]], [[Vijayakumar (actor)|Vijayakumar]], Padmapriya ||\n|-\n| Thunai Iruppal Meenakshi || ||[[Valampuri Somanathan]] || [[Vijayakumar (actor)|Vijayakumar]], [[Sujatha (actress)|Sujatha]] ||\n|-\n| [[Bhuvana Oru Kelvi Kuri]] || Nagarajan ||[[S. P. Muthuraman]] || [[Rajinikanth]], [[Sumithra (actress)|Sumithra]], || Remade in Malayalam as [[Munnettam]]\n|-\n| [[Sri Krishna Leela (1977 film)|Sri Krishna Leela]] || Lord Krishnan ||[[A. P. Nagarajan]] || [[Jayalalithaa]], [[Srividya]] ||\n|-\n| [[Aattukara Alamelu]] || || R. Thyagarajan || [[Sripriya]] ||\n|-\n| Durga Devi || ||[[Ra. Sankaran]] || [[Srividya]] ||\n|-\n| Sainthadamma Sainthadu || ||[[Devaraj\u2013Mohan]] || [[Sridevi]] ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"8\" | 1978\n| Radhai Ketra Kannan || || R. Krishnamurthy || [[Srividya]] ||\n|-\n| Maariyamman Thiruvizha || || N. Venkatesh || [[Sujatha (actress)|Sujatha]] ||\n|-\n| Kaipidithaval || ||[[A. Bhimsingh]] || [[Sujatha (actress)|Sujatha]] ||\n|-\n| [[Chittu Kuruvi]] || ||[[Devaraj\u2013Mohan]] || [[Sumithra (actress)|Sumithra]], Meera ||\n|-\n| Kannamoochi || || R. Pattabiraman || [[Latha (actress)|Latha]], [[Sumithra (actress)|Sumithra]] ||\n|-\n| [[Kannan Oru Kai Kuzhandhai]] || || N. Venkatesh || [[Sumithra (actress)|Sumithra]], [[Sowcar Janaki]] ||\n|-\n| Machanai Paatheengala || ||[[V. C. Guhanathan]] || [[Sumithra (actress)|Sumithra]], [[Sridevi]] ||\n|-\n| Athaivida Ragasiyam || || Kiruba Shankar || [[Fatafat Jayalaxmi]] || \n|-\n| rowspan=\"8\" | 1979\n| Ennadi Meenakshi || || K. Narayanan || [[Sripriya]] || \n|-\n| [[Kadavul Amaitha Medai]] || ||[[S. P. Muthuraman]] || [[Sumithra (actress)|Sumithra]] ||\n|-\n| [[Rosaappo Ravi